# Politics

<p>First, a note of self-congratulation: this is a dangerous section for a service like Blot to have. Running a service like Blot involves making decisions that are intensely political. I do try to read deeply and think deeply about everything I do with Blot.</p>

<p>If there's something you think I ought to read, or something you ought to tell me, please <a href="/contact">contact me</a>.</p>
